cs350f20project.controller.command.structural

Class CommandStructuralUncouple

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs350f20project.controller.command.A_Command
      • cs350f20project.controller.command.structural.A_CommandStructural
        • cs350f20project.controller.command.structural.CommandStructuralUncouple

  • public class CommandStructuralUncouple
extends A_CommandStructural
    Defines an UNCOUPLE structural command as defined by the project specifications. When called before COMMIT, the role is static and this is a structural command; after commit, the role is dynamic and this is a behavioral command. There is no distinction is usage or implementation, but in conceptual design, they do differ.
